ely many) of parameters in\nthe functional dependence on the shape of the boundary, and the duality is only\nslightly violated, which allows one to call this violation an anomaly.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 11 Mar 2008 19:50:45 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 29 May 2008 17:41:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2008-11-26"}
